Class YMLComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.nektodev.wikimart.worker.YMLComparator

  • public class YMLComparator
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to compare to files with offer objects. Use StAX because it simple, fast, and not in-memory parsing

      • parseOldFile

        private void parseOldFile()
                   throws javax.xml.stream.XMLStreamException,
                          java.lang.InterruptedException
        Parsing old file, creating Offer object and put if to TreeMap for comparing with "new file" objects.
        Also put object to queue for PictureCheckWorker for checking picture availability
        Throws:
        javax.xml.stream.XMLStreamException
        java.lang.InterruptedException
        See Also:
        parseNewFile()

      • parseNewFile

        private void parseNewFile()
                   throws javax.xml.stream.XMLStreamException,
                          java.lang.InterruptedException
        Parse new file and compare Offers with objects in TreeMap. If there is no object with such id, set modifier to "n", add it to TreeMap and queue for picture availability check.
        If found this object - compare prices, and if price changes, set modifier to "m"
        Throws:
        javax.xml.stream.XMLStreamException
        java.lang.InterruptedException
        See Also:
        parseOldFile(), Offer
